OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRents soar in towns as     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftenants priced out of      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcities                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Towns within commuting distance of     
OL,6, major cities have seen some of the     
OL,7, biggest rent rises of the last three   
OL,8, years, new research suggests.          
OL,10,FThe cost of new lets rose by more than 
OL,11,Fa third in areas such as Bolton,       
OL,12,FNewport and Bradford between 2020 and  
OL,13,F2023, property portal Zoopla said.     
OL,15,FAlthough Glasgow, London, Manchester   
OL,16,Fand Edinburgh also saw big rises, new  
OL,17,Fworking patterns have made an impact.  
OL,19,FWorking from home has allowed some to  
OL,20,Frent bigger places further from cities.
